videos.headline: Doege runs in for short West Virginia TD
videos.description: Jarret Doege finds an open lane and runs into the end zone for a one-yard West Virginia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Doege runs in for short West Virginia TD) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Brewer finds Sneed for Baylor TD
videos.description: Charlie Brewer connects with R.J. Sneed in the end zone for a seven-yard Baylor touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Brewer finds Sneed for Baylor TD) 2020/010/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Bernard makes remarkable juggling INT for Baylor
videos.description: Terrel Bernard intercepts Jarret Doege's pass, bobbles the ball and still comes down with it.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Bernard makes remarkable juggling INT for Baylor) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Leddie Brown squeezes in for short WVU TD
videos.description: Leddie Brown pushes through traffic and falls into the end zone for a West Virginia touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Leddie Brown squeezes in for short WVU TD) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: WVU player tackles his own teammate
videos.description: West Virginia's Alec Sinkfield tries to catch a punt, but teammate Bryce Ford-Wheaton runs into him, causing a fumble.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (West Virginia player tackles his own teammate, forcing muffed punt) 2020/10/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Baylor's Fleeks' 34-yard reception ties game late
videos.description: Charlie Brewer connects with Josh Fleeks for a clutch late-game 34-yard touchdown, which would send the game to overtime.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Baylor's Fleeks' 34-yard reception ties game late) 2020/10/03 ESHEET
